snippet.title: NES Homebrew Game - Lan Master
snippet.description:
Download the game: http://shiru.untergrund.net/files/nes/lan_master.zip

This is my first NES Game, developed in 2010-2011. Participated in NES Coding Compo 2011, got 2nd place there.

The game is released into Public Domain, along with the source code. You can find source code and more related stuff on my website: http://shiru.untergrund.net/

Although I didn't released the game on actual cartridges, you can try to get it there: http://www.thenesdump.com/
